      <ownedComment xmi:id="4e1a2fe3-e772-4fa7-82ba-1a4bcc4da964" body="The {xor} constraint is applied to a set of associations, specifying that&#xA;over that set, exactly one is manifest for each associated instance. Xor is&#xA;an exclusive or (not inclusive or) constraint." annotatedElement="15bc29ed-edb2-4806-9473-0efcd840da8b">
